currentQuests.name: The Killing Fields
currentQuests.description: Farmer Saldean wants you to kill 5 Harvest Watchers.

currentQuests.name: Goretusk Liver Pie
currentQuests.description: Salma Saldean needs 3 Goretusk livers to make a Goretusk Liver Pie.

currentQuests.name: Westfall Stew
currentQuests.description: Verna Furlbrow wants you to deliver her recipe for Westfall Stew to Salma Saldean.

currentQuests.name: Gold Dust Exchange
currentQuests.description: Bring 4 Gold Dust to Remy "Two Times" in Goldshire. Gold Dust is gathered from Kobolds in Elwynn Forest.

currentQuests.name: A Threat Within
currentQuests.description: Speak with Marshal McBride.

currentQuests.name: Further Concerns
currentQuests.description: Marshal Dughan wants you to speak with Guard Thomas.

currentQuests.name: A Rogue's Deal
currentQuests.description: Deliver the Nondescript Letter to Innkeeper Renee in Tirisfal Glades.

currentQuests.name: Vanquish the Betrayers
currentQuests.description: Kill 2 Kul Tiras Sailors, 2 Kul Tiras Marines and Lieutenant Benedict and return to Gar'Thok in Razor Hill.

currentQuests.name: Carry Your Weight
currentQuests.description: Furl Scornbrow in the Razor Hill watchtower wants 3 Canvas Scraps.

currentQuests.name: Break a Few Eggs
currentQuests.description: Bring 3 Taillasher Eggs to Cook Torka in Razor Hill.

currentQuests.name: Report to Orgnil
currentQuests.description: Speak with Orgnil Soulscar in Razor Hill.

currentQuests.name: A Solvent Spirit
currentQuests.description: Bring 2 Intact Makrura Eyes and 3 vials of Crawler Mucus to Master Vornal in Sen'jin Village.

currentQuests.name: Thwarting Kolkar Aggression
currentQuests.description: Lar Prowltusk outside of Sen'jin Village wants you to destroy the 3 sets of Attack Plans held within Kolkar Crag.

currentQuests.name: Practical Prey
currentQuests.description: Bring 3 Durotar Tiger Furs to Vel'rin Fang in Sen'jin Village.

currentQuests.name: Minshina's Skull
currentQuests.description: Retrieve Minshina's skull from the circle of power on the Echo Isles. Bring it to Master Gadrin in Sen'jin Village.

currentQuests.name: The New Horde
currentQuests.description: Report to Gornek in the Den.

currentQuests.name: Cutting Teeth
currentQuests.description: Kill 3 Mottled Boars then return to Gornek at the Den.

currentQuests.name: Vile Familiars
currentQuests.description: Kill 3 Vile Familiars. Return to Zureetha Fargaze outside the Den.

currentQuests.name: Sarkoth
currentQuests.description: Kill Sarkoth and bring his claw back to Hana'zua.

currentQuests.name: Burning Blade Medallion
currentQuests.description: Bring the Burning Blade Medallion to Zureetha Fargaze, outside The Den.

currentQuests.description: Report to Gornek in the Den.
